This paper discusses the structure of neural networks, which is a topic that falls under the category of machine learning and artificial intelligence. Specifically, the paper focuses on the relationship between the depth and width of neural networks, which is relevant to the sub-categories of neural networks (cs.NE), deep learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and systems and control (cs.SY).
